### SimpleApi1 — Webhook Publisher
### Run SimpleApi1 on port 5248, SimpleApi2 on port 5249

@Publisher = http://localhost:5248
@Receiver  = http://localhost:5249

###─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
### STEP 1: Register SimpleApi2 as a webhook subscriber
###  → Use the SAME secret configured in SimpleApi2/appsettings.json Webhook:Secret
###─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
POST {{Publisher}}/webhooks/subscribe
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "url": "http://localhost:5249/webhook/receive",
  "secret": "dev-secret-change-in-production-min-32-chars!!",
  "eventTypes": ["*"]
}

###─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
### STEP 2: List all active subscriptions (secrets shown as ***)
###─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
GET {{Publisher}}/webhooks/subscriptions

###─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
### STEP 3: Trigger a manual test event
###  → Fires immediately to all "*" subscribers
###─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
POST {{Publisher}}/webhooks/trigger
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "eventType": "trigger.test",
  "data": {
    "message": "hello from SimpleApi1 publisher",
    "sentAt": "2026-03-02T10:00:00Z"
  }
}

###─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
### STEP 4: Fetch weather — also fires "weather.fetched" webhook to all subscribers
###─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
GET {{Publisher}}/weatherforecast

###─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
### STEP 5: Delete a subscription (replace {id} with the ID from STEP 1 response)
###─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# DELETE {{Publisher}}/webhooks/subscriptions/{id}

###─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
### Health & Info
###─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
GET {{Publisher}}/health

###
GET {{Publisher}}/info
